&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1097&quot; data-local-id=&quot;74af45c3ae33&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Power electronics control:&lt;/strong&gt; Write and tune the firmware that commands inverters, chargers, and battery systems to convert and move electrical energy correctly, safely, and efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
