&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;680&quot; data-local-id=&quot;f550669b8784&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Board bring-up:&lt;/strong&gt; Take freshly fabricated carrier boards from freshly assembled to reliably booting — methodically proving out power, memory, and communication interfaces, hands-on with hardware on the bench.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;890&quot; data-local-id=&quot;97cd6816a629&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Bootloader &amp;amp; kernel configuration:&lt;/strong&gt; Stand up the bootloader and configure the Linux kernel so it correctly recognizes and drives our specific hardware.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
